<paragraph id="8CABB3416DB1A0897AB4787A4EED0344" pageId="0" pageNumber="43">Comments.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="307A9063DA5BCB7D159DFD33508B5452" pageId="0" pageNumber="43">This genus includes 60 species, mainly distributed in eastern Asia. Half of them are recorded from China, but there are still 13 species known only from females in China, and three from males. Most of them (ten species) are recorded from Yunnan Province. No species were recorded from Jiangxi Province.</paragraph>
